{"tid":490750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[入黎幫下眼]鄭明筠失蹤8日 哥哥盼網民助尋人","createTime":"2017-12-06T02:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T02:30:28.000Z","uid":88681,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ecf56bcc9a6935ec7fd8210cd54bf1833a31ddea","tid":490750,"uid":88681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171205/large/1512485577_a073.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171205%2Flarge%2F1512485577_a073.jpg&h=59df0dfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【22:30】鄭明筠兄長訪問<br />\n<br />\n37歲女子鄭明筠於上月28日下午離開沙田水泉澳邨住所後便告失蹤，其家人於上月30日向警方報案。她身高約1.6米，體重約50公斤，瘦身材，方面型，黃皮膚及蓄長直黑髮，最後露面時身穿黑色長袖上衣、黑色長褲、黑色運動鞋、戴黑色頭箍及攜有一個橙色背包。<br />\n鄭女的胞兄晚上向《蘋果》表示，胞妹為聾啞人士，上周二(28日)她自稱獨自在尖沙嘴美麗華行街，曾與他用WhatsApp聯絡，但未有異樣。鄭明筠當晚沒有回家，並曾與父母用Wechat聯絡，一度暗示自己已長大，父母誤以為她去朋友家過夜。至翌日(29日)早上9時許，鄭明筠一度於fb上線，其後便離線，直至上周四(30日)鄭兄與父母在尖沙嘴至油麻地一帶尋找，可惜沒有發現。鄭明筠失蹤至今已有8日，家人憂心忡忡，盼網民協助尋人。<br />\n警方呼籲，任何人如有鄭明筠的消息或曾見過她，請致電3661 1173或9872 4791，或電郵至 rmpu-nts-1@police.gov.hk 與新界南總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171205/57545206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171205%2F57545206&d=Dj16aHTGWLAWY3FyFSablm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=109a01ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171205%2F57545206&h=3568cdd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171205/57545206</a>"},{"pid":"fec76d7774078764cb8cf46e5ccca0bfd21170b3","tid":490750,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bc22365803a40b70aa5e4a3324ade41063c1c20","tid":490750,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"37歲黎講,算OK"},{"pid":"8ed8796baf25a694e8f806d33d6ce85cc8003b4a","tid":490750,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:30:28.000Z","msg":"長大啦"}]}